{
  "stem": "9102.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember having gone there once or twice with-- not even with my parents, but with the neighbors downstairs who lived on the second floor.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Before the war?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, before the war, no.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because it was, yeah, quite a large district in Amsterdam, the Jewish district, really.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What, by the way, is all broken down now and completely disappeared.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was quite active.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, you know, we all-- we went quite often down there to visit because one of my father's brothers lived near there, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He, he was a principal of one of the schools and, you know, we went to visit him quite often.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as far as I remember, we-- I went to kindergarten, uh, what was-- as it happened to be the location of that kindergarten was just behind the museum, or museum, I would say the-- the building where later on the Jewish people were all gathered before they were put on transports.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But just as it happened to be, but of course I went to that kindergarten before the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was in 19-- when did I go to kindergarten, you know, up to '38, '39 I guess.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then in 1940 I went to, when I turned six I went to the normal school to start grade one.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And as it turned out I went just there for, I guess, one and a half years.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that time the Germans stopped, you know, Jewish people going to school, and that's how it was.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I never attended any more than the, you know, first and part of the second grade.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Nazism, that of course came up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know my-- not really.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was too young, really, to realize what that was.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
